---

<section id="blog" class="blog-preview section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Blog</span>
    <h2 class="blog-headline">Thoughts & Insights</h2>
    <p class="blog-subtitle">
      Articles on brand strategy, marketing, and creative leadership
    </p>

    <div class="coming-soon">
      <div class="coming-soon-icon">‚úç</div>
      <h3>Coming Soon</h3>
      <p>
        I'm working on sharing insights from my experience in brand strategy and creative marketing. Check back soon for articles on building memorable brands.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .blog-preview {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .blog-headline {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .blog-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .coming-soon {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-12);
    background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .coming-soon-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .coming-soon h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .coming-soon p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
